TEST CASES FOR Register 

Test Case 1 :

Description: Verify mandatory field validation

Steps:

1) Attempt to submit the registration form with missing required fields (e.g., name, email, password).

Expected Result:

Error messages are displayed for each missing mandatory field.


Test Case 2:

Description: Verify password strength requirements

Steps:

1) Enter a password that does not meet the strength requirements (e.g., too short, no special characters).

Expected Result:

An error message is displayed, indicating the password requirements.

Test Case 3:

Description: Verify successful account creation

Steps:

1) Fill in all required fields with valid information.
2) Click the "Register" button.

Expected Result:

Account is successfully created and a confirmation message is displayed.
